{"id":232967465,"title":"我媽不肯承認買錯口罩😰","content":"https://i.imgur.com/0gWMaiz.jpg\n\n如題 我媽訂了一堆防霾口罩，我很認真的看了那項產品的訊息真的就是不符合肺炎防範的標準，跟她說了還生氣...\n而且還是當護士的遠房阿姨推薦她買的(？)，到底是出了甚麼問題 好無語😕\n\n口罩已經下訂了，我覺得是消耗品所以買錯了也沒關係以後還能用，但我媽一直堅持那也可以防細菌，她的理由是口罩可以防微粒而且是當護士的阿姨推薦的...\n還是其實真的可以？但我看介紹也沒寫醫療用品認證的那串號。\n\n目前家裡是還沒買到盒裝大量的口罩，去了好市多屈臣氏也沒貨，只在超商跟全聯買小包的用，想說再等一陣子過完年工廠開工就會有貨了...吧？好不安 畢竟我對SARS那時期完全沒印象","excerpt":"如題 我媽訂了一堆防霾口罩，我很認真的看了那項產品的訊息真的就是不符合肺炎防範的標準，跟她說了還生氣...，而且還是當護士的遠房阿姨推薦她買的（？），到底是出了甚麼問題 好無語，口罩已經下訂了，我覺得","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"255fd275-fec2-49d2-8e46-2e1557ffaeb0","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-27T13:33:22.996Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-27T13:47:52.566Z","commentCount":9,"likeCount":14,"tags":[],"topics":["口罩","傻眼","醫療"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"閒聊","forumAlias":"talk","school":"國立聯合大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":12},{"id":"514c2569-fd53-4d9d-a415-bf0f88e7329f","count":2}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/0gWMaiz.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"cc1e94f0-de08-45f9-870d-be88e0cc45ad","url":"https://i.imgur.com/0gWMaizl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/0gWMaizl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/0gWMaizl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-27T13:33:22.996Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-27T13:47:52.566Z"},{"id":"cc1e94f0-de08-45f9-870d-be88e0cc45ad","url":"https://i.imgur.com/0gWMaiz.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/0gWMaiz","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/0gWMaizl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-27T13:33:22.996Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-27T13:47:52.566Z"}],"postAvatar":""}